{"id":31751,"date":"2019-06-03T12:52:29","date_gmt":"2019-06-03T08:52:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=31751"},"modified":"2019-06-03T12:52:29","modified_gmt":"2019-06-03T08:52:29","slug":"sufyan-hadith-misguide-fiqh","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/sufyan-hadith-misguide-fiqh\/","title":{"rendered":"Sufyan on Fiqh: Hadith cause misguidance, except for scholars of Fiqh"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Al-Qayrawani reported: Sufyan ibn \u2018Uyaynah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe prophetic Hadith cause misguidance, except for the scholars of Fiqh.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Ja\u0304mi\u2019 fi\u0304 al-Sunan wal-\u0100da\u0304b 1\/118<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u064a\u0631\u0648\u0627\u0646\u064a \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0633\u0641\u064a\u0627\u0646 \u0628\u0646 \u0639\u064a\u064a\u0646\u0629 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b \u0645\u064e\u0636\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0629 \u0625\u0644\u0627 \u0644\u0644\u0641\u0642\u0647\u0627\u0621<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">1\/118 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0627\u0645\u0639 \u0641\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0646\u0646 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0622\u062f\u0627\u0628 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0645\u063a\u0627\u0632\u064a \u0648\u0627\u0644\u062a\u0627\u0631\u064a\u062e<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Al-Qayrawani reported: Sufyan ibn \u2018Uyaynah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe prophetic Hadith cause misguidance, except for the scholars of Fiqh.\u201d Source: al-Ja\u0304mi\u2019 fi\u0304 al-Sunan wal-\u0100da\u0304b 1\/118 \u0639\u0646 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3712,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout"