hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12186,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/14\/ibn-wahb-fiqh-malik-layth\/","url_meta":{"origin":31751,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Wahb on Fiqh: I would be led astray, if not for Imam Malik","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Dhahabi reported: Ibn Wahb, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWere it not for Malik and Al-Layth, I would have been ruined. I used to believe that everything narrated about the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, should be acted upon.\u201d Source:\u00a0Siyar A\u02bbla\u0304m al-Nubala\u0304\u02bc 8\/148 Ibn Abi Layla\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/13\/sufyan-rukhsah\/","url_meta":{"origin":31751,"position":2},"title":"Sufyan on Fatwa: Granting proper concessions, not strictest opinion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Usamah reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIndeed, knowledge in our view is granting a proper concession upon a reliable basis. As for giving the strictest opinion, anybody can do that well.\u201d Source: Ja\u0304mi\u2019 Baya\u0304n al-\u2018Ilm 1467 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0623\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0651\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32539,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/28\/amash-hadith-fiqh-doctors\/","url_meta":{"origin":31751,"position":3},"title":"A\u2019mash on Hadith: Fiqh scholars are doctors, Hadith scholars pharmacists","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubaydullah ibn \u2018Amr reported: We were with Al-A\u2019mash, may Allah have mercy on him, while he was asking Abu Hanifa about legal issues and Abu Hanifa answered him. Al-A\u2019mash said to him, \u201cFrom where did you get this?\u201d Abu Hanifa said, \u201cYou narrated to us from Ibrahim as such. You\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37408,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/22\/salaf-fatawa\/","url_meta":{"origin":31751,"position":4},"title":"Salaf on Fatwa: Hesitancy in legal verdicts unless necessary","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 22, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mu\u2019afa ibn \u2018Imran reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI met the jurists and they disliked to answer a question or a request for a legal verdict. They would not issue a legal verdict unless no one else could be found, then they would give their\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25304,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/ahmad-follow-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":31751,"position":5},"title":"Ahmad on Sunnah: Do not blindly follow me, follow Hadith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abdul Barr reported: Imam Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAl-Awza\u2019i had opinions, Malik had opinions, Sufyan al-Thawri had opinions. Each of them had opinions, and it is all the same to me. Indeed, the proof is only in the narrations.\u201d In another narration, Imam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/31751","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=31751"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/31751\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=31751"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyh